name: Last night's dream
description: I'm thirsty, it's hard to move, like I'm in slow motion. I look up and see something blurry... it's moving. Is it moving? I try to crawl to get a better look at what it is. I get close enough to give it shape, it's a statue... or what's left of it. It's not moving, it's the light, coming from nowhere, illuminating it and swirling around it. What am I seeing? Do I like it? or am I afraid of it?
